#!/bin/bash
YELLOW='\033[1;33m'
NC='\033[0m'
echo -e "${YELLOW}處理器資訊 (CPU Information)${NC}"
if [[ "$(uname)" == "Darwin" ]]; then
    echo "- Model: $(sysctl -n machdep.cpu.brand_string)"
    echo "- Cores: $(sysctl -n hw.ncpu)"
else
    echo "- Model: $(grep -m1 "model name" /proc/cpuinfo | cut -d: -f2 | sed 's/^ //')"
    echo "- Cores: $(nproc)"
fi
